title: Waving Canadian flags, French 'freedom convoy' gets underway - Reuters
content:
1. Waving Canadian flags, French 'freedom convoy' gets underway  Reuters

  3. Freedom Convoy organizer ‘downright disgusted’ by media coverage, American trucker blasts ‘disconnected’ press  Fox News
  4. The whole world should be worried by the ‘siege of Ottawa’. This is about much more than a few anti-vaxx truckers  The Guardian
  5. Canadian Trucker Says Protesters Blocking His Route 'Making Us Look Bad'  Newsweek

description: Protesters set out from southern France on Wednesday in what they call a "freedom convoy" that will converge on Paris and Brussels to demand an end to COVID-19 restrictions, inspired by demonstrators who have blocked a Canadian border crossing.
